title: Spanish Bayonet with a Tree and Five other Plant Studies, Jamaica
description: Horizontal view of a series of botannical studies with at top left a leafy plant, at top center a bough with flowers and leaves, at top right two stems with veined leaves, at top far right a fern in small scale, at bottom left a Spanish bayonet tree, at bottom center left boughs, at bottom center right a stem with leaves, and a far right asix foot tree.
